          img(src="@images/home/desktop/illustration-passionate.svg", alt="illustration")
        div.image-text-block__content
          h3.image-text-block__heading Passionate
          p.image-text-block__paragraph Each project starts with an in-depth brand research to ensure we only create products that serve a purpose. We merge art, design, and technology into exciting new solutions.
          .image-text-block 
      .image-text-block
        div.image-text-block__img-container.image-text-block__img-container--180deg
          img(src="@images/home/desktop/illustration-resourceful.svg", alt="illustration")
        div.image-text-block__content
          h3.image-text-block__heading Resourceful
          p.image-text-block__paragraph Everything that we do has a strategic purpose. We use an agile approach in all of our projects and value customer collaboration. It guarantees superior results that fulfill our clientsâ€™ needs.

